pb_preserves_mono_step
----------------------

l1: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ mono f $ by ax
l2: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ ∀ y ((f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ f ∘ y) → (h ∘ alpha ~ y)) $ by all_elim [l1]
l3: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ (f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ f ∘ (h ∘ beta)) → (h ∘ alpha ~ h ∘ beta) $ by all_elim [l2]
l4: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ pullback f g h k $ by ax
l5: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ f ∘ h ~ g ∘ k $ by and_elim_l [l4]
l6: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ alpha) $ by comp_right [l5]
l7: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ f ∘ (h ∘ beta) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ beta) $ by comp_right [l5]
l8: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta $ by ax
l9: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ g ∘ (k ∘ alpha) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ beta) $ by comp_left [l8]
l10: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ beta) $ by mor_trans [l6, l9]
l11: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ g ∘ (k ∘ beta) ~ f ∘ (h ∘ beta) $ by mor_sym [l7]
l12: $ ∀ x ∀ y ((f ∘ x ~ f ∘ y) → (x ~ y)) , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ f ∘ (h ∘ beta) $ by mor_trans [l10, l11]
l13: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ h ∘ alpha ~ h ∘ beta $ by imp_elim [l3, l12]
l14: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ ∀ x ∀ y ∀ z ((f ∘ x ~ g ∘ y) → ((h ∘ z ~ x) → ((k ∘ z ~ y) → (z ~ pb_med f g h k x y)))) $ by and_elim_r [l4]
l14a: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ ∀ y ∀ z ((f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ g ∘ y) → ((h ∘ z ~ h ∘ alpha) → ((k ∘ z ~ y) → (z ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ alpha) y)))) $ by all_elim [l14]
l14b: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ ∀ z ((f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ alpha)) → ((h ∘ z ~ h ∘ alpha) → ((k ∘ z ~ k ∘ alpha) → (z ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ alpha) (k ∘ alpha))))) $ by all_elim [l14a]
l14c: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ (f ∘ (h ∘ alpha) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ alpha)) → ((h ∘ alpha ~ h ∘ alpha) → ((k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ alpha) → (alpha ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ alpha) (k ∘ alpha)))) $ by all_elim [l14b]
l15: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ h ∘ alpha ~ h ∘ alpha $ by mor_refl 
l16: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ alpha $ by mor_refl
l17: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ (h ∘ alpha ~ h ∘ alpha) → ((k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ alpha) → (alpha ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ alpha) (k ∘ alpha))) $ by imp_elim  [l14c, l6]
l18: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ alpha) → (alpha ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ alpha) (k ∘ alpha)) $ by imp_elim [l17, l15]
l19: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ alpha ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ alpha) (k ∘ alpha) $ by imp_elim  [l18, l16]
l20: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ ∀ y ∀ z ((f ∘ (h ∘ beta) ~ g ∘ y) → ((h ∘ z ~ h ∘ beta) → ((k ∘ z ~ y) → (z ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) y)))) $ by all_elim [l14]
l20a: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ ∀ z ((f ∘ (h ∘ beta) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ beta)) → ((h ∘ z ~ h ∘ beta) → ((k ∘ z ~ k ∘ beta) → (z ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta))))) $ by all_elim [l20]
l20b: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ (f ∘ (h ∘ beta) ~ g ∘ (k ∘ beta)) → ((h ∘ beta ~ h ∘ beta) → ((k ∘ beta ~ k ∘ beta) → (beta ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta)))) $ by all_elim [l20a]
l21: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ h ∘ beta ~ h ∘ beta $ by mor_refl
l22: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ k ∘ beta ~ k ∘ beta $ by mor_refl
l23: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ (h ∘ beta ~ h ∘ beta) → ((k ∘ beta ~ k ∘ beta) → (beta ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta))) $ by imp_elim  [l20b, l7]
l24: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ (k ∘ beta ~ k ∘ beta) → (beta ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta)) $ by imp_elim [l23, l21]
l25: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ beta ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta) $ by imp_elim[l24, l22]
l26: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ alpha) (k ∘ alpha) ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta) $ by pb_med_congr [l13, l8]
l27: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ alpha ~ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta) $ by mor_trans [l19, l26]
l28: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ pb_med f g h k (h ∘ beta) (k ∘ beta) ~ beta $ by mor_sym [l25]
l29: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ alpha ~ beta $ by mor_trans [l27, l28]

pb_preserves_mono
-----------------

l1: $ mono f , pullback f g h k , (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) ⊢ alpha ~ beta $ by pb_preserves_mono_step
l2: $ mono f , pullback f g h k ⊢ (k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) → (alpha ~ beta) $ by imp_intro [l1]
l3: $ mono f , pullback f g h k ⊢ ∀ beta ((k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) → (alpha ~ beta)) $ by all_intro [l2]
l4: $ mono f , pullback f g h k ⊢ ∀ alpha ∀ beta ((k ∘ alpha ~ k ∘ beta) → (alpha ~ beta)) $ by all_intro [l3]
